  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK862">
<l>aṉpila ṉāṉṟa tuṇaiyilaṉ ṟāṉṟuvvā </l>
<l>ṉeṉpariyu mētilāṉ ṟuppu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>How can he who is unloving, destitute of powerful aids, and himself without strength overcome the might of his foe ?</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
